The '''Barani List''' was created by [[Neil Barani]].

The list contained information on the conspiracy pertaining to the [[Yen-2]] mining outpost. Vigo [[Color/Legends|Green]] provided the false information to Neil Barani and hoped that Barani would sell it to the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Empire]] and bring down [[Sprax]]'s operation along the [[Sisar Run/Legends|Sisar Run]]. However, Green and Barani failed. The list was recovered by [[Guri]], who later killed Green.

